{
  "stem": "20089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we were very fortunate in having Miss Richman at the head of UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gertrude Richman, R-I-C-H-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a lady at that time, a social worker from Washington, age I would say in her late 40s.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very, very vivacious, very interested in the survivors, and very sympathetic of their needs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think it was her empathy which made Rosenheim run very efficiently.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The AJDC supplied a lot of the Jewish needs, but under-supplied the food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the supplies depended on the numbers of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we got in an extra group of children, we got extra supplies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When a group of children were transferred to another camp, the numbers were less.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know whether this is relevant or not, but during my stay in Germany and in Munich, rather in Rosenheim, I was asked by Seal, the AJDC Director, to go to another camp to supervise elections.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And really not elections so much as have a census of the number of people at a camp that was being opened.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because some more had come through from-- from Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was sent to this place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't remember the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was a-- a small-- a small camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the people who were doing the census were the displaced persons, one of the seniors of the displaced persons and AJDC.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was towards the end of my stay, at about I would say in about December 1947.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was quite interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it had-- it was at a place that I hadn't been before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
